 ','line_number':1,'multiline':True]['text':' To ensure that we kill the shutdown operation during step down, we wait','line_number':30,'multiline':False]['text':' until we hit the 'hangInShutdownBeforeStepdown' failpoint.','line_number':31,'multiline':False]['text':' The parallel shell exits while shutdown is in progress, and if this happens early enough,','line_number':63,'multiline':False]['text':' the primary can still accept connections despite successfully starting to shutdown.','line_number':64,'multiline':False]['text':' So, retry connecting until connections cannot be established and an error is thrown.','line_number':65,'multiline':False]['text':' We need to ensure that the primary that is shutting down completes the shutdown','line_number':72,'multiline':False]['text':' process before attempting to stop the set.','line_number':73,'multiline':False]